{"tid":931256,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華府據報調查華為利用滙控違規交易","createTime":"2018-12-07T01:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T02:05:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd1ca9cca5f7a2ec3d9df8f12a79c9dd0fbe801","tid":931256,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/12/07/2009823_6921cabc5d8582375746de76cbd7a917.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F12%2F07%2F2009823_6921cabc5d8582375746de76cbd7a917.jpg&h=7ce91431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路透引述消息人士稱，華為副董事長孟晚舟被捕，是美國調查華為利用全球銀行體系以逃避美國制裁伊朗行動的一部分。據悉，美國早在2016年開始調查華為有沒有違反美國制裁伊朗禁令，近期則把滙控(00005)納入調查範疇，以調查華為有否利用滙控進行違規交易。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，消息人士指出，滙控本身不是今次調查對象。<br />\n<br />\n滙控在2012年與美國檢察官就違反美國禁令與洗黑錢法例，達成遞延認罪協議及罰款19.2億美元。滙控發言人拒評上述消息。<br />\n<br />\n截至本港今早4時8分，滙控在美國的預託證券(ADR)股價折合報64.95港元，比香港昨日收市低1.63%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2009823/華府據報調查華為利用滙控違規交易\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2009823%2F%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93&d=RGtujUXDJSHD%2FDnQ12ZO02xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=f201e964\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2009823/華府據報調查華為利用滙控違規交易</a>"},{"pid":"5c70102b31266726c8e2aa744c52da20ec786a5b","tid":931256,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:00:04.000Z","msg":"又要炒IT9黎填返條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c3eafd04f43b7e6c53a0beaf8f659b920a0229","tid":931256,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:02:07.000Z","msg":"快d 制裁香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c9a1c6507c3d10b47dded30ac87